long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Play other games on the top-left menu.
🎵 Jump, fly, and dash your way through the pulse-pounding world of Geometry Dash Official! 🕹️ Immerse yourself in the iconic rhythm-based platformer that challenges your reflexes and creativity. 🔥 With this official Chrome extension, experience the original Geometry Dash gameplay directly in your browser! Master each level, overcome obstacles, and groove to the electrifying soundtrack that defines the game. 🚀 Whether you're a seasoned player or a newcomer, Geometry Dash Official delivers an adrenaline-packed adventure that keeps you on the edge of your seat. Get ready to dash to the beat and conquer the geometry! 🌈🔷
